4 "Meet Captain America", Sebastian Montes, Paul Giacoppo,  October 24 2010 (2010-10-24), 004

A compilation of the micro-series episodes "Meet Captain America", "The Red Skull Strikes!", "If This Be Doomsday!", and "Lo, There Shall Come a Conqueror".  

Captain America leads an assault on a HYDRA facility.
Captain America and Bucky come face to face with the Red Skull. 
HYDRA's scheme to win World War II backfires.
Kang the Conqueror discovers that his timeline is somehow being destroyed by Captain America.

Introducing characters: 

Captain America, Kang the Conqueror, Red Skull, Bucky, Abraham Erskine, 
Chester Phillips, Wolverine, Howling Commandos (Jack Fury, Dum Dum Dugan, Gabe Jones, Rebel Ralston, 
Dino Manelli, Izzy Cohen, Pinky Pinkerton), Ymir, Ravonna
